==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: magnetosphere
<hw>mag*net"o*sphere</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the magnetic
field of a planet; the volume around the planet in which charged
particles are subject more to the planet's magnetic field than to the
solar magnetic field.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.6</source>]</p>

